R\big{[}\frac{n-2}{4(n-1)} + \sum_{k=1}^{\infty}\sum_{i=k}^{\infty}\frac{c_{ki}\lambda^i}{\epsilon^{k}}\big{]}
\hspace{2.5in} 
$$

$$
